description.p:
(1) the number of figure elements (the number of registered elements) which are determined as part of the continuous-line-group after they are retrieved by the shape-corrected branch element retrieval unit 213 having the element-to-be-trimmed retrieval unit 214 or the connected-element retrieval unit 215;


(2) a pointer (original figure element ID) to the ID of the determined figure element stored in the figure element storage DB 114 or the figure element ID stored in Table 1;


(3) ID of a corrected figure element (new figure element ID); and


(4) a correction process type either of a trimming correction process and a connection correction process.
